@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = REPLACE_WITH_BEARER_TOKEN
@incidentId = REPLACE_WITH_INCIDENT_ID

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

< ./sample_payloads/register.json

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

< ./sample_payloads/login.json

### Current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Submit incident triage
POST {{baseUrl}}/incidents/triage
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

< ./sample_payloads/triage_incident.json

### List incidents
GET {{baseUrl}}/incidents?skip=0&limit=20

### Search incidents
GET {{baseUrl}}/incidents/search?query=fight&incident_type=&severity=High&skip=0&limit=20

### Nearby incidents
GET {{baseUrl}}/incidents/nearby?lat=1.3521&lng=103.8198&radius_m=5000&limit=20

### Alerts feed
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/feed?lat=1.3521&lng=103.8198&radius_m=5000&limit=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Log alert event (responding)
POST {{baseUrl}}/alerts/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

< ./sample_payloads/alert_event_responding.json

### Log alert event (open)
POST {{baseUrl}}/alerts/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

< ./sample_payloads/alert_event_open.json